Namibia - _Mycoplasma mycoides_ subsp. _mycoides_ SC (inf. with) (contagious bovine pleuropneumonia [CBPP])
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
General information
Report type: immediate notification
Started: 11 Aug 2022
Confirmed: 11 Aug 2022
Reported: 11 Oct 2022
Reason for notification: recurrence
Last occurrence: 7 Nov 2021
Causal agent: _Mycoplasma mycoides_ subsp. _mycoides_ SC (MmmSC)
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

Outbreak location 1: Amaupa, Ruacana, Omusati
Date of start of the outbreak: 11 Aug 2022
Epidemiological unit: village
