Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Killed and disposed of / Slaughtered or killed for commercial use / Vaccinated
Cattle / 15 / 1 / 0 / - / - /

Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: contact with infected animal(s) at grazing/watering points

Control measures at event level
Domestic control measures applied: vaccination in response to the outbreak(s); traceability; surveillance within the restricted zone; surveillance outside the restricted zone; screening; movement control; ante and post-mortem inspections

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type / Species / Test / First result date / Last result date / Result
Windhoek Central Veterinary Laboratory / cattle / complement fixation test for antibody detection (Ab CFT) / 11 Aug 2022 / 5 Oct 2022 / positive

